{"tid":293481,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人幫幫手做DSE放榜義工?","createTime":"2017-06-22T07:57:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-23T06:05:13.000Z","uid":46047,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ba16d07690bfeb420f667d35618ef4d2fb22cdbe","tid":293481,"uid":46047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:57:16.000Z","msg":"見到招義工唔好罵我住其<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實每年放榜我地都會喺舊登招班義工幫幫應屆DSE考生排Jupas同其他服務<br />\n今年放榜我地都會喺高登連登做放榜輔導同幫手排Jupas<br />\n<br />\n過去每年都會有十幾個巴絲打嚟幫手，但其實遠遠唔夠人，因為實在太多巴絲打需要排JUPAS<br />\n所以過去都辛苦左大家，好感激佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望今年會招到多返D義工幫手<br />\n<br />\n如果熟DSE就更好，唔熟嘅唔緊要，因為我地會提供一個Training 講解DSE同埋排JUPAS原則<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但至少巴絲一定要經歷DSE先，如果唔係好難做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果大家放榜嗰個星期某D日子可以幫手，希望可以黎到幫手<br />\n<br />\n大家可以填一填個表先，我會再聯絡你地傾下實質係點~<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/pZnSYd\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FpZnSYd&d=TqiXZQoAFblHPQJEzl5ZAP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=0ce76228\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/pZnSYd</a>"},{"pid":"b1e2dd68ef416fc7ead927951e7e1c4be2ecdcdb","tid":293481,"uid":46047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T08:07:28.000Z","msg":"放返上年我地啲Ｊ圖先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/22/160720_133f0392725894ebfb03ff4aa7c6faca.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F22%2F160720_133f0392725894ebfb03ff4aa7c6faca.png&h=a4576c32&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"421fad5c862c2500c6f0a636400ee5771d96c8c2","tid":293481,"uid":46047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T09:05:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9944d3944a87509220279f45941475124606c8e5","tid":293481,"uid":23902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T09:14:21.000Z","msg":"留名比人幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd11851c8a6412fda8ad34050d809bd1ade2fe30","tid":293481,"uid":46047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T09:39:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d15a634a71a99cb09ec9ab588d0411bf20670a7e","tid":293481,"uid":73285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T14:11:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e3ddf2e3c510e397dada43d112f8916f5939ddeb","tid":293481,"uid":28309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T14:33:39.000Z","msg":"lm 做啲咩的"},{"pid":"c0b82ea38101ae6dc73359743de572d226a6848c","tid":293481,"uid":87780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T14:35:58.000Z","msg":"你個訓練中心咁遠又搞咁夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fd1f2d1595b89fd433505760acc2bab4f8daa41","tid":293481,"uid":46047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T06:04:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你個訓練中心咁遠又搞咁夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無計，其實都係一次咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋想就返D岩岩放工放學既人"},{"pid":"6f9630a6eb069fcfe8e7eb8977a0fb8ddae8f871","tid":293481,"uid":46047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T06:04:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>lm 做啲咩的</blockquote><br />\nDSE放榜時侯<br />\n我地會有聽Call 同 網上幫人情緒支援 / 排Jupas<br />\n有關知識都會喺Training會教大家基本概念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"965c29d47211d01dd2ad2eaf79a008e2bd24139e","tid":293481,"uid":46047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T06:05:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Tg:Hygsrhvx</blockquote><br />\n巴打，如果可以既<br />\n可以填填張表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 感謝你"}]}